                        <h3 class="head-font aside-header">Luke 23:45&ndash;46<span class="superref"> 1</span></h3>
                        <!-- piece body -->
                        <p>How majestic is your<span class="superref"> 2</span> name in all the earth;<span class="superref"> 3</span></br>
                        You set<span class="superref"> 4</span> deep<span class="superref"> 5</span> before<span class="superref"> 6</span> the loom.<span class="superref"> 7</span></br>
                        I, knowing not<span class="superref"> 8</span> such<span class="superref"> 9</span> fathoms<span class="superref"> 10</span> &mdash; save<span class="superref"> 11</span> found<span class="superref"> 12</span> commune<span class="superref"> 13</span> hemmed<span class="superref"> 14</span> &mdash;</br>
                        lie<span class="superref"> 15</span> within gaping<span class="superref"> 16</span> viscera.<span class="superref"> 17</span></br>
                        In such<span class="superref"> 18</span> found one;<span class="superref"> 19</span></br>
                        Your love endures forever<span class="superref"> 20</span> &mdash;</br>
                        Lord, how majestic is your name in all the earth!<span class="superref"> 21</span></p>
                        <hr>
