                        <p class="flg29-ref"><span class="superref">5</span> a. A <span class="flg29-bold">weighty</span> and <span class="flg29-bold">inarticulate resonance</span> which is <span class="flg29-bold">low</span> in pitch and timbrally full-bodied.</br>
                        <span class="flg29-indent">b. <span class="flg29-bold">Rom. 8:22&ndash;27</span></span></br>
                        <span class="flg29-indent">c. <span html lang="el">&tau;&alpha;&rho;&#940;&sigma;&sigma;&omega;</span>: to put into motion by stirring up and troubling. (<span class="flg29-bold">John 11:33; John 12:27;</span> Luke 24:37&ndash;38)</span></br>
                        <span class="flg29-indent">d. <span class="flg29-bold">Ps 88</span></span></br>
                        <span class="flg29-indent">e. <span class="flg29-bold">Luke 22:41&ndash;42</span></span></br>
                        <span class="flg29-indent">f. <span class="flg29-bold">Ps. 22; Matt. 27:27&ndash;46</span></span></br>
                        <span class="flg29-indent">g. The ocean.</span></p>
                        <p class="flg29-ref"><span class="superref">6</span> a. <span class="flg29-bold">Matt. 14:25&ndash;32</span></br>
                        <span class="flg29-indent">b. <span class="flg29-bold">Ps. 23:5&ndash;6</span></span></p>
                        <p class="flg29-ref"><span class="superref">7</span> a. <span class="flg29-bold">Ps. 139:1&ndash;12</span></br>
                        <span class="flg29-indent">b. A machine for weaving yarn into fabric.</span></br>
                        <span class="flg29-indent">c. An <span class="flg29-bold">incomprehensible deep sense</span> of <span class="flg29-bold">awe</span> and <span class="flg29-bold">dread.</span></span></p>
                        <p class="flg29-ref"><span class="superref">8</span> <span class="flg29-bold">Ps. 139:6</span></p>
                        <p class="flg29-ref"><span class="superref">9</span> a. The aforementioned notion.</br>
