                        <p class="flg29-ref"><span class="superref">10</span> a. <span html lang="el">&#972;&rho;&gamma;&upsilon;&iota;&#940;</span>: a measure of depth, roughly the length of outstretched arms which is 5-6 ft. (Acts 27:27&ndash;44 ESV)</br>
