                        <p class="flg29-ref"><span class="superref">14</span> a. <span class="flg29-bold">Luke 8:43&ndash;48</span></br>
                        <span class="flg29-indent-dub">b. <span class="flg29-bold">Ps. 139:5&ndash;6</span></span></br>
                        <span class="flg29-indent-dub">c. The folded and sewn edge of fabric.</span></p>
                        <p class="flg29-ref"><span class="superref">15</span> a. <span class="flg29-bold">Isa. 43:1&ndash;7</span></br>
                        <span class="flg29-indent-dub">b. <span class="flg29-bold">Ps. 16</span></span></br>
                        <span class="flg29-indent-dub">c. <span class="flg29-bold">Consolation</span> in through which one is <span class="flg29-bold">tended</span>, while <span class="flg29-bold">remaining</span> in a particular orientation.</span></p>
                        <p class="flg29-ref"><span class="superref">16</span> a. Zech. 12:10; John 19:34</br>
