                        <span class="flg29-indent-dub">c. The fullest <span class="flg29-bold">cup</span> which resounds a <span class="flg29-bold">death rattle.</span> (<span class="flg29-bold">1 Cor. 11:23&ndash;26</span>)</span></br>
                        <span class="flg29-indent-dub">d. An extensively vast perforation through which something pours out.</span></p>
                        <p class="flg29-ref"><span class="superref">17</span> a. <span html lang="el">&sigma;&pi;&lambda;&#940;&gamma;&chi;&nu;&alpha;</span>: the <span class="flg29-bold">profoundly elemental</span>, and <span class="flg29-bold">unrestrained affections</span> which are felt in the <span class="flg29-bold">innermost bowels</span>. (2 Cor. 6:11&ndash;13; Acts 1:18)</br>
                        <span class="flg29-indent-dub">b. Innards.</span></p>
